videos.description: Will Hart's punt is blocked and the ball slips out of Notre Dame LB Jonathan Jones' hands to return possession to Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Notre Dame fumbles blocked punt) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Notre Dame fumbles blocked punt

videos.description: Michigan's Zach Charbonnet scores a seven-yard touchdown to put the Wolverines up 10-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Charbonnet runs in 7-yard Michigan TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charbonnet runs in 7-yard Michigan TD

videos.description: Zach Charbonnet finds the end zone again, this time with a one-yard run to put Michigan up 17-0.
videos.headline: Charbonnet scores another TD

videos.description: Ian Book finds Cole Kmet jogging into the end zone for a 7-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan fans throw towels after ND scores wide-open TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan fans throw towels after ND scores wide-open TD

videos.description: Donovan Peoples-Jones slides across the end zone while catching Shea Patterson's eight-yard pass to put Michigan up 24-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Peoples-Jones makes sliding TD grab) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Peoples-Jones makes sliding TD grab

videos.description: Shea Patterson finds Nico Collins with a 16-yard touchdown pass to put Michigan up 31-7 over Notre Dame.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan pours it on with Collins' TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan pours it on with Collins' TD

videos.description: Shea Patterson blocks for Tru Wilson's 27-yard touchdown run as Michigan continues to run up the score on Notre Dame.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (QB Patterson blocks for Wilson’s 27-yard TD run) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: QB Patterson blocks for Wilson's 27-yard TD run

videos.description: Dylan McCaffrey, younger brother of NFL star Christian McCaffrey, finds Mike Sainristil who takes it the rest of the way for another Michigan touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McCaffrey throws 1st TD of the season) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCaffrey throws 1st TD of the season
